videos.description: Ty Jerome dishes to Jack Salt in traffic and he finishes with a two-handed dunk early in the first half.
videos.headline: Virginia's Jerome feeds Salt for slam

videos.description: Oshae Brissett speeds down the court and throws down an epic two-handed slam against No. 2 Virginia.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Brissett explodes to rim for dunk

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter connects with Kyle Guy who drills a three-pointer from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Virginia's Guy scores from deep

videos.description: Ty Jerome gets caught in traffic inside so he dishes it out to Ty Jerome, who knocks in the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Wilkins battles, finds Jerome for triple

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu finds Marek Dolezaj, who rises up for a two-handed jam early in the second half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's  Dolezaj throws it down

videos.description: Jack Salt receives the lob from Kyle Guy and rises up for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Guy connects with Salt for the alley-oop slam

videos.description: Syracuse's Marek Dolezaj steals the ball and feeds Frank Howard, who throws it down in the second half.
videos.headline: Cuse capitalizes on Virginia turnover for a flush

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter speeds down the court and spins before hitting a layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hunter goes coast-to-coast for nifty bucket

videos.description: Brian Oliver and Evan Lepler applaud Virginia's intensity on both offense and defense in the Cavaliers' 59-44 victory over the Orange.
videos.headline: No. 2 Virginia executes on both sides against Syracuse
